{"id":556666,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/04/【异闻观止】共青团中央教你如何做正规审查/","date":"2017-04-17T05:07:47Z","modified":"2017-04-17T05:07:47Z","title":"【异闻观止】共青团中央教你如何做“正规”审查","content":"<p><strong>原标题：知乎的“政治敏感” 到底是谁的“政治敏感”呢？</strong></p>\n<p>今天早些时候，团团兴冲冲地发了一篇攒了好久文字的回答，心里头幻想着这回答这么用心总有个千把赞吧。等了一会，发现好像没有知友愿意点赞，结果打开一看，顿时如遭晴天霹雳：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-a555393507986da317573171378b78ba_b.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556670\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-a555393507986da317573171378b78ba_b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-a555393507986da317573171378b78ba_b.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-a555393507986da317573171378b78ba_b-169x300.png 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-a555393507986da317573171378b78ba_b-576x1024.png 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>竟然<b>被政治敏感</b>了！</p>\n<p>虽然如此，然而团团并没有十分愤懑，心里想着：“知乎真是个好网站啊，为了避免广大青少年免遭不良信息的荼毒，居然如此用功。这篇文字好歹也是经过团中央知乎团队诸人审核的，我们的政治敏感性不会如此之差吧？看来还是要加强两学一做啊。”</p>\n<p>于是团团就开始在知乎上闲逛起来，这一逛不要紧，团团看着这一篇一篇的回答，心里是拔凉拔凉的啊。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-c7a4640a9fdbae730845fd121105e065_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556671\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-c7a4640a9fdbae730845fd121105e065_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-c7a4640a9fdbae730845fd121105e065_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-c7a4640a9fdbae730845fd121105e065_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-c7a4640a9fdbae730845fd121105e065_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>公开侮辱人民解放军</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-14f8cac2a41c616c66a497662decd469_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556672\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-14f8cac2a41c616c66a497662decd469_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-14f8cac2a41c616c66a497662decd469_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-14f8cac2a41c616c66a497662decd469_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-14f8cac2a41c616c66a497662decd469_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>公然宣扬<b>种族歧视</b>，<b>为极端种族主义团体张目</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-f843d8ae5bdde063741c425c2b6c4b9d_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556673\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-f843d8ae5bdde063741c425c2b6c4b9d_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-f843d8ae5bdde063741c425c2b6c4b9d_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-f843d8ae5bdde063741c425c2b6c4b9d_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-f843d8ae5bdde063741c425c2b6c4b9d_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>否定共产党搬开三座大山，庸俗化革命目的</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-0ab26c13a15f42df6b37282add61ce45_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556674\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-0ab26c13a15f42df6b37282add61ce45_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-0ab26c13a15f42df6b37282add61ce45_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-0ab26c13a15f42df6b37282add61ce45_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-0ab26c13a15f42df6b37282add61ce45_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>恨国的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-b5590c7d734a27b600f88df6dde4a382_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556675\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-b5590c7d734a27b600f88df6dde4a382_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-b5590c7d734a27b600f88df6dde4a382_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-b5590c7d734a27b600f88df6dde4a382_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-b5590c7d734a27b600f88df6dde4a382_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>逆向民族主义</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-8e7adb064c8418252875078ecebf954f_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556676\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-8e7adb064c8418252875078ecebf954f_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-8e7adb064c8418252875078ecebf954f_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-8e7adb064c8418252875078ecebf954f_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-8e7adb064c8418252875078ecebf954f_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>挑拨民族矛盾</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-493c8aff048647a5cf8d4ef1b6650e05_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556677\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-493c8aff048647a5cf8d4ef1b6650e05_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-493c8aff048647a5cf8d4ef1b6650e05_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-493c8aff048647a5cf8d4ef1b6650e05_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-493c8aff048647a5cf8d4ef1b6650e05_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>为日本侵略者“三光政策”洗地</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-9fcc724537c335f9eb6bc5ed82187c2d_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556678\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-9fcc724537c335f9eb6bc5ed82187c2d_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-9fcc724537c335f9eb6bc5ed82187c2d_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-9fcc724537c335f9eb6bc5ed82187c2d_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-9fcc724537c335f9eb6bc5ed82187c2d_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>否定土地革命</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-7ce352430878a6bcfb319d79ab5aba2f_b.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556679\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-7ce352430878a6bcfb319d79ab5aba2f_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-7ce352430878a6bcfb319d79ab5aba2f_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-7ce352430878a6bcfb319d79ab5aba2f_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-7ce352430878a6bcfb319d79ab5aba2f_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-10ceab7832e88dd2460efb10e758aa15_b.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556680\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-10ceab7832e88dd2460efb10e758aa15_b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-10ceab7832e88dd2460efb10e758aa15_b.png 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-10ceab7832e88dd2460efb10e758aa15_b-169x300.png 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/v2-10ceab7832e88dd2460efb10e758aa15_b-576x1024.png 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><b>公然传播谣言</b>的，不是政治敏感。</p>\n<p>所以说知乎的政治敏感，到底是三角的呢，还是四角的呢？</p>\n<p>或者说，<b>知乎的政治敏感，到底是谁的政治敏感呢</b>？</p>\n<p>真是<b>令人深思</b>啊。</p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;</p>\n<p>本文作者：共青团中央知乎团队 大公无司</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20505],"tags":[16016,30806,9249,25797,14691]}